http://www.nacion.com/nacional/salud-publica/Salud-confirma-circulacion-virus-chikunguna_0_1455454572.html [in Spanish]

Guatemala. 5 Dec 2014. (susp.) 20 553 cases, (conf.) 181 cases; Deaths 4.
http://www.prensalibre.com/noticias/comunitario/suman-cuatro-los-muertos-por-chikungunya-guatemala-zacapa_0_1261074038.html [in Spanish]

Honduras (Comayagua department). 27 Nov 2014. (registered) 168 cases; Municipalities most affected: Villa de San Francisco, Choluteca.
http://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/1062073.registran-en-honduras-168-casos-de-chikungunya.html [in Spanish]

